data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 10, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104yog1665702628229.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/yog1665702628229.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/yog1665702628229.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"yog1665702628229\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      FocusIndicator\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Determines how the Checkbox shows that it has focus.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"yog1665702628229__topic_d103895e1_d103896e1_d103897e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"yog1665702628229__p_d103898e1_d103899e1_d103900e1\">FocusIndicator<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code><code class=\"ph codeph\">flash</code> | <code class=\"ph codeph\">hot</code> |\n               <code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">off</code></p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"yog1665702628229__p_d103901e1_d103902e1_d103903e1\">Example: <code class=\"ph codeph\">\"FocusIndicator=flash\"</code>\n</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"yog1665702628229__table_d12251e1_d12252e1_d12253e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"yog1665702628229__table_d12251e1_d12252e1_d12253e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Value</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"yog1665702628229__table_d12251e1_d12252e1_d12253e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Description</p>\n</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"yog1665702628229__table_d12251e1_d12252e1_d12253e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">flash</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"yog1665702628229__table_d12251e1_d12252e1_d12253e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">The widget flashes when the input focus is on the Checkbox.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"yog1665702628229__table_d12251e1_d12252e1_d12253e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">hot</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"yog1665702628229__table_d12251e1_d12252e1_d12253e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">The widget shows Windows hot state when the input focus is on the\n                           Checkbox. This means that the color of widget is changed when the widget\n                           has input focus.</p>\n<p class=\"p\">Not applicable when running on a Windows machine that is running in\n                           Classic mode.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"yog1665702628229__table_d12251e1_d12252e1_d12253e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">off</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"yog1665702628229__table_d12251e1_d12252e1_d12253e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">The associated label of the checkbox shows the focus. If there is no\n                           label, there is no focus indicator for the Checkbox. Default.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section table\" id=\"yog1665702628229__section_w836ab1b5b3_w837ab1b5_w838ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1173572e162\">Usage</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"yog1665702628229__table_d11987e1_d11988e1_d11989e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Dynamic?</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Yes</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Supported in Grid?</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">No</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Dependencies:</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">None</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"yog1665702628229__section_uhg_fpn_wwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1173572e208\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"yog1665702628229__p_d103910e1_d103911e1_d103912e1\">Use this property if the Checkbox does not have an\n            associated label so that the end user can still see which field in the Form has\n            focus.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"yog1665702628229__section_pn2_gpn_wwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1173572e217\">Applies To</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"yog1665702628229__ul_plr_3pn_wwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"yog1665702628229__li_d41651e1_d41652e1_d41653e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"fxi1688449052174.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fxi1688449052174.html\" title=\"The ucheckbox widget enables the user to set a Boolean value in a form component. Uniface provides a logical widget called CheckBox, which is mapped to ucheckbox.\">ucheckbox (CheckBox)</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3617208\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3617208\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "FocusIndicator Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 10, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 FocusIndicator Determines how the Checkbox shows that it has focus. FocusIndicator = flash | hot | off Example: \"FocusIndicator=flash\" Value Description flash The widget flashes when the input focus is on the Checkbox. hot The widget shows Windows hot state when the input focus is on the Checkbox. This means that the color of widget is changed when the widget has input focus. Not applicable when running on a Windows machine that is running in Classic mode. off The associated label of the checkbox shows the focus. If there is no label, there is no focus indicator for the Checkbox. Default. Usage Dynamic? Yes Supported in Grid? No Dependencies: None Description Use this property if the Checkbox does not have an associated label so that the end user can still see which field in the Form has focus. Applies To ucheckbox (CheckBox) Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}